                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3312" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0448</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11703 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小步慢走 or 大步快行？——步步高的财务管理体系转型决策</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Piecemeal steps or long strides?——BBG’s decision on the transformation of its financial management system</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周兰，王善平，陆才吉，袁宏巨，程义斐，陈宇涵，胡文馨，刘宇蔚</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">步步高商业连锁股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智慧零售；财务共享中心；财务管理体系转型；2018百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">smart retailing; financial shared service center; transformation of financial management system</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例主要描述了步步高为适应发展战略，在财务共享中心的赋能下，所面临的财务管理体系转型是“小步慢走”还是“大步快行”的决策选择。创立于1995年的步步高是全渠道多业态零售的领跑者，伴随着大数据时代的到来，2017年，步步高开始立足于多业态、全渠道智慧零售的发展战略，其现有“双层式金字塔”型财务管理体系重核算、轻战略，难以匹配公司发展。步步高于2014年建立财务共享中心，效率提升和人员转型驱动着步步高财务管理体系的整体转型。本案例为步步高财务管理体系转型设计了两个方案，是选择基于现有体系升级的“双层倒椎”型体系，还是选择全新的“三核两翼”式体系，成为了步步高面临着的决策难题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case mainly described that BBG is enabled by the financial shared service center to make a strategic choice between “piecemeal steps” and “long strides” on the transformation of its financial management system, accommodating to its development strategy. Founded in 1995, BBG has always been the frontrunner in the omni-channel, multi-format retailing. In 2017, the dawn of the big data era, BBG started to establish a development strategy based on the omni-channel, multi-format retailing; however, BBG’s “double-layer pyramid” financial management system focused too much on accounting instead of development strategy, making it inapplicable to BBG’s overall development. Built in 2014, BBG’s financial shared center has prompted the overall transformation of BBG’s financial management system through improved efficiency and personnel adjustment. This case study has devised two different systems for BBG on the transformation of its financial management system —— an elevated “reversed double-layer taper” system based on the original one or a brand-new “three cores and two wings” system, thus making BBG faced with an unprecedented decision making problem.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司理财》、《高级财务管理》、《管理会计理论与实务》、《公司战略》、《风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务管理体系</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
